description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of Bloomberg Barclays 2023 Maturity Corporate Index which composed of U.S. dollar-denominated, investment-grade corporate bonds maturing after March 31, 2022 and before April 1, 2023.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities (including indirect investments through an underlying fund) of the underlying index, and may invest up to 10% of its assets in certain futures, options and swap contracts, cash and cash equivalents, as well as in securities not included in the underlying index.
